data.description: Beautifully renovated, bright, and spacious brick ranch! This 1600 square foot, 3 bedroom, 2 full bath spacious home features with stainless steel appliances, granite countertops with glass tile backsplash. This Beautiful ranch style home also has a sunroom in the back of the home. The property has a driveway on each side of the house, a carport, and a shed.   VA Assumable Loan at 2.6% interest rate.
